Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我通過全世界媒體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想向日前要求引渡羅德·吉普利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並對我國發起攻擊的PLANT最高評議會議長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾伯特·狄蘭達爾先生傳達訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉克絲·克萊茵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Cosmos的盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個向PLANT發射核彈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用大規模殺傷兵器燒燬城市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把孩子當成戰爭機器的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼奧布不惜戰鬥也要袒護他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們對它…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要被她的形象所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉克絲·克萊茵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她人會在奧布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣長相 一樣聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一樣名字的人在狄蘭達爾議長身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我身為西蓋爾·克萊茵之女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次大戰中與Archangel並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也和那時一樣與那艘船一同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在奧布的阿斯哈代表身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她和我不同 信念也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先要告訴大家這點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有支持狄蘭達爾議長的言行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止這邊的放送
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管了快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被他們牽著鼻子走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不戰也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯全在煽動戰爭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡商人Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議長的話是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是真相嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是自然人 也不是Coordinator
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯的是他們 世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要陷入為自己開脫的語言陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然我並不打算袒護吉普利爾氏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即聯繫奧布政府
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而也不相信狄蘭達爾議長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須看得更清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狄蘭達爾議長真正的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有兩個拉克絲·克萊茵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在奧布…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 再派一艘穿梭機 立刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是個事故
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止是你 我也吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底為何會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在只好稍微改變一下計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊才是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是狄蘭達爾議長…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZAFT不是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壞的是Logos和聯合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧布是他們的同夥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰讓我們受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是誰解放了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧布是聯合的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰信站在他們一邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你暫時藏身起來較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會虧待你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你世界才能真正得救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和民眾也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我絕不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以只是很短一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 拉克絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們按計劃去Messiah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球的聯合軍動向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 目前還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 世事真是難料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 雖說是冒牌貨…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別問我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一頭霧水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 唯一清楚的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的長官不是拉克絲·克萊茵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是受她的命令行事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊司令部來電
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva歸航卡潘塔利亞後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即出發與月球艦隊會合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這 這下又突然要上天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個奧布的拉克絲·克萊茵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼連你也這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣迷惑我們正是敵人的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕大家都會這樣在意真偽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺有深度的心理戰嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼人會在意這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為真的就都是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假的就是邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎那些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議長是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這個就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起那些 我們還有其他必須考慮的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom和阿斯蘭·薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯蘭?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯蘭…是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活著待在Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛這機體的就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…梅琳也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅琳也還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但若活著 也就有可能在那艘船裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gounod距離預定地點還有20分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem發電機運轉率85%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,23號至55號 臨界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能量傳輸良好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超鏡面反射器 臨界偏差3129
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預備冷卻器GR啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管道連接
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 您真的要發射這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是為此才特地前來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的話真值得信賴 甚感寬心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們在這種地方勤奮工作也有所回報
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近以需要為由斥巨資建造
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵時刻又不敢發射的軟弱政治家太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來我們軍人到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不由得會這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是總統那種膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是狄蘭達爾那種夢想家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該出手時就出手 為了保護
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘖 和報告一樣為數不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是到底為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 不過肯定不是什麼友好設施
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:11:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12宙域有奇怪舉動?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是在防衛警戒區域外 行動有所遲緩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說有圓柱型殖民地在緩慢移動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向PLANT嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 雖然距離還有很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往警戒的玖爾隊 賈尼斯隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前正和其護衛艦隊作戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後這個報告為最優先事項
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gounod 到達指定位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,採取制動了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faure、Czerny
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姿勢穩定 力場展開中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem發電機啟動中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離臨界點480秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 想幹什麼勾當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 總之阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繞到引擎部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑塞克來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的移動殖民地有後續報告嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為目的不明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以命令玖爾隊憂先考慮阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,護衛艦隊從射線軸撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aprilius
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是警告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準 PLANT首都Aprilius
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輸入目標地點 Aprilius
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最終保險解除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全發電機提升至臨界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一樂章 準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem系統發射準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擊發器開啟 開始倒計時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離發射 T-35
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射權給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始彈奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狄蘭達爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獻給你們的Requiem
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.72,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem:鎮魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球背面高能量體發生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全軍撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光束彎曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏來的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Januarius 1到4號直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,December 7號8號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為受到Januarius 4號撞擊損毀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Januarius?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 Gounod的發射角偏離了計算值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是戰鬥的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓Aprilius逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Januarius?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有December?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從月球背面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到用這種方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提亞哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打下這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有第二發的話這次PLANT真的完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都得打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Januarius 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吉普利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從月球背面發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁我們照常警戒正面Arzachel基地的空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daedalus竟然有這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會是從背面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在廢棄殖民地中搭載了大型能量偏向裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分數段扭曲光束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個系統不論炮口在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據扭曲點數量和位置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能指哪打哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔的工藝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這 這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放跑吉普利爾 是我們的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼放跑吉普利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論怎麼說 我們當時必須殺死他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 出擊準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家接連作戰一定很累
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到關鍵時刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不努力就無家可歸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎最大 Minerva出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和Genesis的時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經無可救藥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 PLANT當然是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事大家肯定也厭惡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 被打後還擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後又被打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種戰鬥的連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在無法斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都想幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為此只有戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們參加戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議長恐怕想為這個世界展示一種全新的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議長說的沒有戰爭的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們不再有紛爭的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人天生由遺傳基因決定一切的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用遺傳基因?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Destiny Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天生的遺傳基因決定人們的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不稱職的人淘汰、調整、管理的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淘汰 調整?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確可以使大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從自己無法預知未來的不安中解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無憂無慮的生活也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以自己能決定的命運為代價
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盼望得到一切力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類出於這種祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於開始對遺傳基因動手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們Coordinator社會的究極形態
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏恐怕不會有戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為知道戰鬥也是徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的命運會告訴你是徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道這點而生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在這種社會中扮演什麼角色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命運才是王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是遺傳基因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他算神官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是徒勞的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不做徒勞之舉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 才沒那麼容易死心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:21:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.81,0:22:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上天吧 阿斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須阻止議長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創造未來的不是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支離破碎的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未能保護的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能允許這種事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦再發生就無法實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悔恨化作憤怒時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次覺醒的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.11,0:23:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士Gundam Seed Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變革的序曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賭上一切出擊! Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:23.13,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,握った拳の強さで砕けた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:33.73,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,願いに血を流す掌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:43.78,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,果てない翼と鎖は良く似て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:54.90,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,重さで何処にも行けずに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:04:04.20,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,亡くすばかりの幼い瞳で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:14.72,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,人は還らぬ星を想う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:24.66,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,掲げたそれぞれの火を 命と咲かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:30.43,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,運んで行くことが運命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:45.04,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,輝き刻む 誰もが優しい 刻の傷痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:23.13,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,緊握的雙拳粉碎了夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:33.73,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,鮮血染紅了雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:43.78,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,無盡的雙翼如同枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:54.90,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,沉重得去飛不到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:04:04.20,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡充滿了幼小的眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:14.72,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,星星承載著失去的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:24.66,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,讓生命 像紛紛燃起的火焰般綻放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:30.43,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉動不會停息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:45.04,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,把人們溫柔的光輝 化作時間的傷痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:06.76,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,君の姿は僕に似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:16.18,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,静かに泣いてるよに胸に響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:27.62,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,何も知らないほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:31.37,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,幸せというけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:38.46,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕はきっと滿足しないはずだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:44.67,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕が選んだ今を生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:48.22,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,それだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:55.77,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,君の速さは僕に似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:59.48,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,齒止めのきかなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:03.17,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,空が怖くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:10.92,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕はいつまで頑張ればいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:20.83,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,二人ならば終わらせることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:06.76,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身影與我有幾分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:16.18,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,猶如靜靜的哭泣在心中迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:27.62,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:31.37,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:38.46,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻無法滿足於此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:44.67,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,接受自己選擇的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:48.22,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:55.77,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,你的速度與我有幾分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:59.48,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,當一切無法停止時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:03.17,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,開始害怕天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:10.92,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我要奮鬥到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:20.83,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人的話就會讓它結束

